Program: The Why Factor
Title: The Moon
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p022m7bf
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 21 Jul 2014
The moon has fascinated humans everywhere and for all time. Why? Mike Williams explores the moon in culture, how it affects life on Earth and he asks Alan Bean – one of the handful of people who have walked on it – what the moon is really like. Producer: Richard Knight (Image shows a full moon as seen from the sky at night. Credit: AFP/Getty Images) Show less